description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if Formula 1 (F1) racer Charles Leclerc finishes 2nd in driver standings for the 2022 F1 season. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

As soon as the results for the final scheduled race of the 2022 F1 season are known (the final scheduled race for the 2022 season is presently scheduled for November 18-20 in Abu Dhabi: https://www.formula1.com/en/racing/2022.html), this market may resolve.

If the 2022 F1 season does not end by November 30, 2022, 11:59:59 PM ET, this market will resolve according to the standings available then.

The primary resolution source for this market will be official information from Formula 1 (ex: https://www.formula1.com/en/results.html/2022/drivers.html).
